      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a simple way to get from A to B? This car is in poor condition and definitely shows its age with significant wear, but it offers a great opportunity for a mechanic or someone looking for a fixer-upper at a very accessible price!",
