    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. While the engine starts consistently and the car is roadworthy, the transmission occasionally shifts roughly, and there are several cosmetic blemishes including minor door dings and some interior upholstery wear. It has been maintained adequately, but the buyer should expect to invest in some suspension work and new tires in the near future. This is a solid, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few imperfections.",
