    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected without any known mechanical issues. While the interior is clean and the body is solid, you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age. Overall, it is a reliable, road-ready car that provides a great balance of performance and value.",
